{"tid":1078102,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【估國家】50歲單身男挖地洞，用鐵環、鐵鏈、電棍囚16歲少女學生性侵24天","createTime":"2019-03-26T05:14:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-26T08:34:05.000Z","uid":79563,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"0a945e774729ad8be15797afa51215f660a6194a","tid":1078102,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T05:14:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190326/large/1553563454_2caf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190326%2Flarge%2F1553563454_2caf.jpg&h=cdb17973&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190326/large/1553563427_6613.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190326%2Flarge%2F1553563427_6613.jpg&h=95c63d27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n湖南鳳凰縣檢察院昨日（25日）通報指，該縣一名50歲單身男子在家中地下挖洞，囚禁一名16歲女生當性奴。檢察院近日已批捕該男子，將發出檢察意見書。<br />\n<br />\n通報透露，涉案的龍姓男子為鳳凰縣山江鎮人，平時靠駕車載客維持生計，因一直單身，經常看色情影片，造成心理扭曲變態，產生禁錮及強姦女子的念頭。他在網上購買鐵環、鐵鏈、電棍、人皮面具和女性假髮等犯案工具。2016年初，他更興建房屋，親手在地下挖開一個地洞，作禁室培慾之用。地下室潮濕，長年不見陽光，地面只放置了一塊木板和膠馬桶，牆面裝嵌鐵環，鐵環上連接5米長的鐵鏈，鐵鏈則扣有5把鐵鎖。<br />\n<br />\n上月13日下午3時許，他在從山江鎮古塘村開車去山江鎮載客，途徑山江鎮「新農村」時，遇到一名16歲女生在路邊招手截車，龍男見女生年輕漂亮，便以「搭順風車」為由接載她，途中訛稱要借手機，將女生的手機據為己有，女生心感不妙，跳車逃跑。龍男下車追趕並毆打她，制服她後用鞋帶綑綁她的手，以膠紙封嘴，再用尼龍袋套其上半身，之後載她回家，將她綁到地下室，用鐵鏈鎖其頸部，並進行多次性侵。<br />\n<br />\n女生失蹤後，其家人到當地派出所報警，警方在24天後救出女生。在案件審查期間，鳳凰縣檢察院檢察官安排心理學家為龍男進行輔導。目前，龍男已被批捕，等待法院開庭聆訊。"},{"pid":"75844f15ef50750051bd10f3a2ec5d06f8059c96","tid":1078102,"uid":243446,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T05:15:50.000Z","msg":"又係蝗國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a33a759da981852f9b32700167a735f9a1549443","tid":1078102,"uid":200202,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T05:16:14.000Z","msg":"仲以為美國"},{"pid":"e83b07799c3a547f4ae5b2ba0f1191b7f4c260b1","tid":1078102,"uid":83251,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T05:17:08.000Z","msg":"以為係印度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88dbeaa48a78243cb439b456844fe0e6834e1f27","tid":1078102,"uid":170249,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T05:17:38.000Z","msg":"支那得分 偉大了我的國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a76ed8532dff2dd06a0d1d4ca4693254ac532be6","tid":1078102,"uid":128591,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T05:17:41.000Z","msg":"蝗國啲公安好少可會做到野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"103bf958192f9d7432e5fa7cb1c4703c5ee35245","tid":1078102,"uid":38777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T05:17:55.000Z","msg":"地獄鬼國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4b173c77221d322ccc2f371353312ddb859168e","tid":1078102,"uid":49853,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a33a759da981852f9b32700167a735f9a1549443","tid":1078102,"uid":200202,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T05:16:14.000Z","msg":"仲以為美國"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T05:18:19.000Z","msg":"美國邊洗挖洞"},{"pid":"ee53ccb11512383b96fdf64dc4d24a75b411d51a","tid":1078102,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T05:22:05.000Z","msg":"臭作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c3c8620cab94579070d20cacf305054047658fd","tid":1078102,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T05:22:08.000Z","msg":"安排心理學家為龍男輔導<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf8a2ed73306229b251c6b70eda279042a117fc3","tid":1078102,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T05:23:40.000Z","msg":"瘋狂凌辱16歲女生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gi